grow_horizontal = 2
text = "This demo scene is set up to show how the Reader can be used to run several seperate conversations in parallel.
This could be used to have passive conversations going on in the background of a game.
Or it could be used to run macro game events like a very basic quest system or trigger points in a story.
You could even trigger a conversation as a result of a trigger in another!"
horizontal_alignment = 1

